ETBI is the representative organisation for Ireland's 16 Education and Training Boards (ETBs). The ETBs are statutory authorities which have responsibility for education and training, youth work and a range of other statutory functions. ETBs manage and operate second-level schools, further education colleges, multi-faith community national schools and a range of adult and further education centres delivering education and training programmes.&#xd;
